ActNational Defence Act
PrecisTerminate the appointment of GENERAL RAYMOND ROLAND HENAULT as Chief of the Defence Staff, effective April 1, 2005; and authorize GENERAL RAYMOND ROLAND HENAULT to accept the appointment as Chairman of the Military Committee of the North Atlantic Treaty Organization, at the rank of General, for a term of three years, effective June 15, 2005.
